Overview of Changes in iterative_refocus 1.0.2:
==================================

* Updated docs
* Reformat the code
* Added examples in the demo/ direcotry
* renamed to refocus-it because of SourceForge requirements

Overview of Changes in iterative_refocus 1.0.1:
==================================

* Makefile for Microsoft Visual C++ added
* Improvements in support of defocus blur
* Added support for regular motion and gaussian blur
* Images with alpha channel supported
